title: Nonfinancial Noncorporate Business; Equipment, Current Cost Basis, Level (DISCONTINUED)
notes:
This series has been discontinued and will no longer be updated. It was a duplicate of the following series, which will continue to be updated: https://fred.stlouisfed.org/series/NNBECBQ027S

The FRED series Equipment and Software - Assets - Balance Sheet of Nonfarm Noncorporate Business is now known as Nonfinancial Noncorporate Business; Equipment and Software, Current Cost Basis.

The source series id is FL115015205.Q.

This series appears in Table B.104. For further information see the assistance provided in the guide to the Flow of Funds at https://www.federalreserve.gov/apps/fof/.
